description: In this clip from www.artistshousemusic.org - Warren Vache is a supremely accomplished, versatile and rare performer. He has been astounding audiences worldwide for decades with his superb cornet, trumpet and flugelhorn stylings. In this segment, Warren and talks about the history of the jazz trumpet.
